{"tid":1886373,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"侵侵開始清算美國國內共匪打手啦","createTime":"2020-02-19T00:52:41.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-20T07:59:14.000Z","uid":326897,"like":126,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"f1dd866da8855e30a50e871266df748df2589c88","tid":1886373,"uid":326897,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T00:52:41.000Z","msg":"美國國務院對5家中國國營傳媒推新規定 上報僱員名單<br />\n2020-02-19 HKT 08:13<br />\n<br />\n美國國務院宣布，對中國5家在美國營運的國營傳媒實施與外國大使館相同的規定，這5家機構包括：新華社、中國環球電視網、中國國際廣播電台、中國日報發行商及人民日報的美國總代理海天發展。<br />\n<br />\n有傳媒取得國務院的文件指出，這5家中國媒體並非獨立的新聞機構，而是<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">受到中國有效控制</span></strong>，嚴控內容及編輯方針，是<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">中共宣傳部門的一部分</span></strong>，因此符合外國使團法規定的外國使團定義，但不會限制這些機構的新聞採訪，仍可以參加國務院的記者會。<br />\n<br />\n國務院規定這5家機構，需要向美國政府披露僱員名單及人事變動，登記所有租用及擁有的物業，租賃及購買前，要事先獲得批准，所有<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">措施即時生效</span></strong>。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1509378-20200219.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1509378-20200219.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=WZLdF6k3LRQ%2Bb7h5E4OoDhSC%2F35X4DTIU%2BW3we%2FDSDs%3D&h=deac9acf\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1509378-20200219.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=10c1d29a\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1509378-20200219.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">侵侵開始清算國內共匪打手啦</span></span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1471121277e65710272479b2e822c5d2c1b90ef6","tid":1886373,"uid":55913,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-